 'https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/studygpt-your-study-copil/fcejkolobdcfbhhakbhajcflakmnhaff?ref=gighub&utm_source=gighub&utm_medium=referral', 'Бесплатно', 'studygpt', 23);
